<title>yswʿ ʿnd qdmyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 jesus, at your feet I sit,
 Near you, where the souls long to be
 It is you, whose word makes me rejoice,
 Guides my walk, and brings solace to my life
 Refrain:
 Oh my master, I will not turn back from loving you
 You are my portion that will never be taken away for me.
 2-
 Jesus, at your feet I worship,
 you are my lord, the God whom I worship.
 You've created me, redeemed me and brought me to life,
 You are my great and glorious God.
 3-
 Jesus, on your feet I pour
 My precious anointment of which you are more precious
 As token of devoting my life to you,
 Declaring my enduring and unceasing love for you

